sentences.english: As requested by disciple Hai Ying below I had written the name of the seal in calligraphy.
sentences.chinese: 应弟子海鹦如下的提请，我已手书一法印的名称了。

sentences.english: An avian veterinarian can perform a blood test to measure your African grey's calcium levels.
sentences.chinese: 兽医可以用验血来衡量你灰鹦的钙水平。

sentences.english: In the air, puffins are surprisingly fleet flyers.
sentences.chinese: 在空中，海鹦也是惊人的飞行健将。

sentences.english: As requested by disciple Hai Ying below, I had written a Dharma sentence into calligraphy.
sentences.chinese: 应弟子海鹦以下的提请，我已将一法句手书成翰墨。

sentences.english: Puffin couples often reunite at the same burrow site each year.
sentences.chinese: 海鹦夫妇每年都会回到同一处洞穴会面。

sentences.english: This puffin was collecting twigs for his nest.
sentences.chinese: 这只海鹦正在为筑巢而收集枝条。

sentences.english: Really the kakapo has a very similar life history to that iconic extinct bird the Dodo.
sentences.chinese: 枭鹦与绝种的渡渡鸟的生命历史十分相似。

sentences.english: Improving your African grey's overall nutrition may alleviate both conditions.
sentences.chinese: 提高您灰鹦的整体营养可能会减轻这两个情况的出现。

sentences.english: Puffins typically hunt small fish like herring or sand eels.
sentences.chinese: 海鹦通常捕食小鱼如青鱼和沙滩鳗鱼。

sentences.english: Pacific puffin having a large yellow plume over each eye.
sentences.chinese: 北太平洋的海鹦，每只眼睛上方有一簇黄色的羽毛。

sentences.english: There are many stories about puffin.
sentences.chinese: 有很多关于海鹦的故事。
